column5: I've been patient.  I'm curious to know what PB means.  I've been lurking the posts to try to deduce what PB means and for a long while I thought that it meant a bass.  Now "PB walleye" pops up and I have to start all over again.
And here I thought we were talking about peanut butter
"Pretty Birdie" "I thought he was just quiet" lol I love that movie!
"We got no food, We got no jobs.........OR PETS HEADS ARE FALLIN OFF!"
ROTFL -- good post, Dabluz, and excellent quotes, Cudz and Blaque
Such a modest reply,   from a guy that belongs to a family of PB.   And you would know anything about these green fish ?????????????????
When you've only been fishing for two years, it's not all that hard to get a PB...they are already slowing down....LOL.
Ok....from what I can see....I'm not the only one who does not know what PB means.
Guess they're all having too much fun to help a frenchman out dabluz.. PB stands for Personal Best !
you spoil sport irishfield lol--lol i was lmao reading the non answers
Hey now...I could have sworn that mikey mikey said that....but then he edited his post....LOL
And all along I thought it meant Perenial Bragging............... Move over Dabluz !!
Thanks irishfield (champs irlandais).  I got a personal message telling me what it was.  My posting above was just my chance to pull somebody's chain....lol.
